  "text": "Cytokine analysis FM supernatants were analyzed for the following cytokines/chemokines using multiplex analysis (BioRad): IL-1b, IL-2, IL-4, IL-6, IL-8, IL-10, IL-12, IL-17, G-CSF (CSF3), GM-CSF (CSF2), IFNg, MCP-1 (CCL2), MIP-1a, MIP-1, b RANTES (CCL5), TNF-a, VEGF and GRO-a as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . FM supernatants were also analyzed for IL-1b by ELISA (R&D Systems).",
